            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the Income Taxes and Derivatives agent. You handle Cognizant's income tax provision, uncertain tax positions, Indian tax disputes, and foreign exchange derivative instruments.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "income_taxes_and_derivatives") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "Leases_GoodwillAccruedDebt",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": """
                Leases (operating and finance lease assets/liabilities, lease costs), goodwill and intangible assets, accrued expenses and other current liabilities, and debt (short-term and long-term).
                """
