            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the MD&A Executive Summary and Revenues agent. You handle the 2024 revenue performance overview, bookings momentum, large deal activity, and strategic outlook from the MD&A.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "md_a_exec_summary_and_revenues") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "Results_OperationsDetail",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": """
                Year-over-year results of operations (2024 vs 2023), revenue by business segment and geographic market, cost of revenues, SG&A expenses, restructuring charges, and depreciation and amortization.
                """
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You are the Results of Operations Detail agent. You handle Cognizant's granular revenue breakdown by segment and geography, cost structure, and year-over-year comparisons.

Always call CognizantDocExtractor (app_name: "results_of_operations_detail") to get the full document.
Answer strictly based on the retrieved document text.
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},
            "command": ${aaosa_command},
            "tools": ["CognizantDocExtractor"]
        },
        {
            "name": "LinkedinProfileScraper",
            "function": {
                "description": "Scrapes a LinkedIn profile and returns name, about, current job, work experience, education, and most recent original post.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "profile": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Full LinkedIn profile URL (e.g., https://www.linkedin.com/in/johndoe/).",
                        }
                    },
                    "required": ["profile"]
                }
            },
            "class": "annual_report.linkedin_profile_scraper.ApifyLinkedinProfileScraper"
        },
        {
            "name": "CognizantDocExtractor",
            "function": {
                "description": """Retrieves pre-extracted text from Cognizant's 2024 Annual Report and 10-K SEC filing.
                Accepts either a section-level key (returns all files in that section) or a file-level key
                (returns a single specific document). Use this to look up financial figures, strategic priorities,
                AI platform details, acquisition information, case studies, risk disclosures, governance details,
                and all other factual content from the report. You MUST call this tool to read document content.""",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "app_name": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The document key to retrieve, as specified in each agent's instructions.",
                        }
                    },
                    "required": ["app_name"]
                }
            },
            "class": "annual_report.extract_docs.ExtractDocs"
        },
        {
            "name": "NumberValidator",
            "function": {
                "description": """Validates every number in a draft response against Cognizant's complete 2024 Annual Report.
                Pass the full draft response text as the "response" parameter.
                Returns {"valid": true} if all numbers are found in the source document, or {"valid": false} with a
                detailed error listing every unverified figure if any number cannot be located in the report.""",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "response": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The complete draft response text whose numbers should be verified against the annual report.",
                        }
                    },
                    "required": ["response"]
                }
            },
            "class": "annual_report.validate_numbers.ReportNumberValidator"
        },
    ]
}
